cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.DB

The paper discusses a system for online privacy that involves an information market, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The system also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and potentially social and information networks (cs.SI) as it involves online advertising. The study also evaluates the feasibility of the market, which could fall under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY) or databases (cs.DB).
